skins.shipDescription: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!
skins.selfIntroduction: My hair? Heheh, I'm virtual so I can change my hair's length whenever I want. How else do you think I look this cool while I'm fraggin' out? I'm the super gamer version of Kizuna AI! Check it!
skins.acquisition: HAI DOMO! Virtual Gamer Kizuna AI here! Don't worry, Commander, I've played AL a whole bunch before! ... Wait, I've become a ship now?!
skins.login: You haven't forgotten about the monthly check in, right? That'd be a real noob move!
skins.details: Are you here to play a game, Commander? I was just about to start streaming one, actually! Would you like to play it with me?
skins.secretaryIdle1: Maybe I'll host the Kizuna AI Cup here! Ayanami and Long Island said they'd be down, so why not be our 4th player, Commander?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Being a genius but in reality playing like a total noob is suffering...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Whoosh! What do you think about this pose I learned from Jamaica? Don't I look cool?
skins.secretaryTouch: You wanna play a round with me? Certainly! I accept your challenge! My skill should not be underestimated!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Commander, do you know what a "headshot" is? Mind if I perform one on you?
